name: GetLinked2me
tag_list: networking, community, social-networking, professional-networking, new-way-of-networking, right-people
overview: Main aim is giving people the option to easily contact to their “right” counterparts on the subject they are interested in. As a result, people will spend less time to expand their social and professional networks and in this sense, efficiency of internet will be increased. Main service will be named as Community Link, hosted under www.GetLinked2me.com domain. There will be no need to download and install a software, system will work directly in web browser. This brand new method of networking will be based on getting people in online events which have pre-determined time limit for each round. If users decide bilaterally that other user / counterpart is the right people, they will be able to add him / her as friend on the site…
